{"tid":1839050,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"菲律賓將135名武漢旅客送返當地","createTime":"2020-01-24T09:04:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T14:21:02.000Z","uid":141151,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a1f344e68c1b3503da5f8d125d2c9cea3416e231","tid":1839050,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:04:21.000Z","msg":"菲律賓將135名武漢旅客送返當地<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504627-20200124.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504627-20200124.htm&d=3ovy23W4cNvxoMUnqPf77QmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=3ffe40d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504627-20200124.htm&h=afc41c71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504627-20200124.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n中國的新型冠狀病毒持續蔓延，菲律賓宣布，會將昨日由武漢抵達卡利波國際機場的135名旅客，全部送返武漢。<br />\n<br />\n卡利波國際機場是進出觀光勝地長灘島的主要途徑。民航官員表示，這批旅客是在菲律賓昨日宣布，暫停來往武漢的航班前，抵達機場，兩間航空公司將會用4班機，將他們送回去。<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓今日開始，要求所有由中國抵達菲律賓的旅客，填寫健康申報表，並要求空中服務員密切觀察旅客是否出現病徵。交通部長強調，因應農曆新年來臨，必須採取一切必要措施防範病毒。"},{"pid":"1a8e1d6a89e6eb5edc25e9ddeb6bce99be367c3c","tid":1839050,"uid":151196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:04:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d79c5f57ac24c52d0f328d744de463f54b4c23","tid":1839050,"uid":262191,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:06:23.000Z","msg":"一個唔洗睇人面色既主權國家一定會咁做"},{"pid":"da6f26bc38b9dcf535335b8086b27a1ba04bb564","tid":1839050,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:12:21.000Z","msg":"送番去仲要封左城 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc5efc4be31388a6069486bbd874de78bebcc58","tid":1839050,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T11:33:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets